---
/**
 * Terms of Service
 * Route: /terms
 */

import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'March 15, 2026';
---

<MainLayout
  title="Terms of Service | Soul Miner's Eden"
  description="Terms of service for Soul Miner's Eden. Policies for orders, delivery, returns, and use of our website."
>
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-warm-900 mb-4">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-warm-500 mb-12">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

      <div class="prose prose-warm max-w-none space-y-8">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-warm-900 mb-4">Agreement to Terms</h2>
          <p class="text-warm-700">
            By accessing or using the Soul Miner's Eden website (soulminerseden.com) or purchasing our products and services, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use our website or services.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-warm-900 mb-4">Products and Services</h2>
          <p class="text-warm-700 mb-4">Soul Miner's Eden provides:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-warm-700">
            <li><strong>Landscape supplies</strong> — compost, mulch, topsoil, and soil blends available for pickup and delivery</li>
            <li><strong>Land management services</strong> — rotational grazing for vegetation management, including solar grazing and agrivoltaic services</li>
            <li><strong>Farm products</strong> — eggs, seasonal produce, and other farm goods available at our farm stand</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-warm-700 mt-4">
            Product availability, pricing, and specifications are subject to change without notice. We make every effort to display accurate product information, but natural products may vary in color, texture, and composition.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-warm-900 mb-4">Orders and Payment</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-warm-700">
            <li>All orders are subject to product availability and confirmation.</li>
            <li>Prices are listed in US dollars and do not include delivery fees unless stated otherwise.</li>
            <li>We reserve the right to refuse or cancel any order for any reason, including pricing errors.</li>
            <li>Payment is due at the time of order unless other arrangements have been made (e.g., contractor accounts).</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-warm-900 mb-4">Delivery</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-warm-700">
            <li>We deliver throughout the Athens-Clarke County area and surrounding communities, typically within 40 miles of our farm in Bogart, GA.</li>
            <li>Delivery fees are based on distance and order size. We will confirm the delivery fee before you place your order.</li>
            <li>We will work with you to schedule a delivery time that works for your project. We ask that someone be available to direct the driver on placement.</li>
            <li>We are not responsible for damage to driveways, lawns, or other surfaces caused by heavy delivery vehicles. Please let us know if you have concerns about access.</li>
            <li>Minimum delivery order is typically 3 cubic yards to keep delivery cost-effective. No minimum for pickup.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-warm-900 mb-4">Pickup Orders</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-warm-700">
            <li>Pickup is available at 189 Luke Road, Bogart, GA 30622 during business hours (Monday–Saturday, 8am–6pm).</li>
            <li>We can load your truck or trailer. Please let us know your vehicle type when ordering so we can prepare accordingly.</li>
            <li>You are responsible for ensuring your vehicle can safely carry the weight and volume of your order.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-warm-900 mb-4">Returns and Satisfaction</h2>
          <p class="text-warm-700">
            Due to the nature of bulk landscape materials, returns are generally not accepted once materials have been delivered or picked up. If you are unsatisfied with the quality of your order, contact us within 48 hours and we will work to make it right. We stand behind the quality of our products.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-warm-900 mb-4">Land Management Services</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-warm-700">
            <li>Grazing and land management services are provided under a separate service agreement specific to each property.</li>
            <li>Service terms, pricing, duration, and scope are outlined in the service agreement provided after your site assessment.</li>
            <li>We carry full liability insurance for all grazing operations.</li>
            <li>Property owners are responsible for disclosing any hazards, easements, or access restrictions on their property.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-warm-900 mb-4">Website Use</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-warm-700">
            <li>You may use our website for lawful purposes only.</li>
            <li>You agree not to submit false information through our forms.</li>
            <li>All content on this website (text, images, logos, design) is owned by Soul Miner's Eden or its licensors and is protected by copyright law.</li>
            <li>You may not reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works from our content without written permission.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-warm-900 mb-4">Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p class="text-warm-700">
            Soul Miner's Eden provides products and services "as is." While we strive for accuracy and quality, we make no warranties, express or implied, regarding the suitability of our products for any particular purpose. Our liability for any claim arising from the use of our products or services is limited to the amount you paid for the product or service in question.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-warm-900 mb-4">Governing Law</h2>
          <p class="text-warm-700">
            These terms are governed by the laws of the State of Georgia. Any disputes shall be resolved in the courts of Oconee County, Georgia.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-warm-900 mb-4">Changes to These Terms</h2>
          <p class="text-warm-700">
            We may update these terms from time to time. Continued use of our website or services after changes are posted constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="bg-warm-100 rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-warm-900 mb-4">Questions?</h2>
          <p class="text-warm-700 mb-4">If you have questions about these terms, we're happy to explain. Just reach out:</p>
          <div class="space-y-2 text-warm-700">
            <p><strong>Soul Miner's Eden</strong></p>
            <p>189 Luke Road, Bogart, GA 30622</p>
            <p>Phone: <a href="tel:+1-706-613-4415" class="text-accent-600">(706) 613-4415</a></p>
            <p>Web: <a href="/contact" class="text-accent-600">Contact Form</a></p>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
